scenes.description: Takanashi Kiara hosts a 3D birthday concert quiz with guests Calliope Mori and Gawr Gura in a picture-in-picture window.

subtitles.original: And by the way, I just recently uploaded a video...
subtitles.english: And by the way, I just recently uploaded a video...

subtitles.original: ...a lore video that explains the whole story behind Casper on my channel.
subtitles.english: ...a lore video that explains the whole story behind Casper on my channel.

subtitles.original: So if you guys are curious, you could go watch that...
subtitles.english: So if you guys are curious, you could go watch that...

subtitles.original: ...if you want to learn more about Casper, mysterious, yes.
subtitles.english: ...if you want to learn more about Casper, mysterious, yes.

subtitles.original: Casper the friendly ghost, yeah, yeah, yeah.
subtitles.english: Casper the friendly ghost, yeah, yeah, yeah.

subtitles.original: At first I hated him, then I loved him.
subtitles.english: At first I hated him, then I loved him.

subtitles.original: Okay, fourth question!
subtitles.english: Okay, fourth question!

subtitles.original: If you get this one right, then you already have...
subtitles.english: If you get this one right, then you already have...

subtitles.original: ...a free dinner with me!
subtitles.english: ...a free dinner with me!

subtitles.original: Thank you for carrying, Calli.
subtitles.english: Thank you for carrying, Calli.

subtitles.original: No problem.
subtitles.english: No problem.

subtitles.original: No, you got this girl, you definitely got the next one.
subtitles.english: No, you got this girl, you definitely got the next one.

subtitles.original: Dude, I don't know if I do got this.
subtitles.english: Dude, I don't know if I do got this.

subtitles.original: Okay, question number four! Da-da-da-da-da, dum!
subtitles.english: Okay, question number four! Da-da-da-da-da, dum!

subtitles.original: How many re-debuts...
subtitles.english: How many re-debuts...

subtitles.original: ...did Takanashi Kiara have?
subtitles.english: ...did Takanashi Kiara have?

subtitles.original: How many re-debuts has Kiara had?
subtitles.english: How many re-debuts has Kiara had?

subtitles.original: Now think before you yell it out loud. Re-debuts.
subtitles.english: Now think before you yell it out loud. Re-debuts.

subtitles.original: Wait, what counts as a re-debut?
subtitles.english: Wait, what counts as a re-debut?

subtitles.original: Well, not debut, but debuts after the re-debut.
subtitles.english: Well, not debut, but debuts after the re-debut.

subtitles.original: I do have a history with re-debuts. It hasn't been one in a while, but...
subtitles.english: I do have a history with re-debuts. It hasn't been one in a while, but...

subtitles.original: ...there was a time where I had many reasons for many re-debuts.
subtitles.english: ...there was a time where I had many reasons for many re-debuts.

subtitles.original: Maybe you know this.
subtitles.english: Maybe you know this.

subtitles.original: My brain wants to say two, but I don't know.
subtitles.english: My brain wants to say two, but I don't know.

subtitles.original: Okay girl, let's brainstorm.
subtitles.english: Okay girl, let's brainstorm.

subtitles.original: All right, let's brainstorm. Do it, faster!
subtitles.english: All right, let's brainstorm. Do it, faster!

subtitles.original: Yeah, ten more seconds!
subtitles.english: Yeah, ten more seconds!

subtitles.original: Oh shit, you remember the first one when the channel got nuked?
subtitles.english: Oh shit, you remember the first one when the channel got nuked?

subtitles.original: The next one was the German one, right? Wait, wait, wait, wait.
subtitles.english: The next one was the German one, right? Wait, wait, wait, wait.

subtitles.original: Okay, so I think it's two.
subtitles.english: Okay, so I think it's two.

subtitles.original: You both think it's two?
subtitles.english: You both think it's two?

subtitles.original: Are you sure?
subtitles.english: Are you sure?

subtitles.original: I think it's two.
subtitles.english: I think it's two.

subtitles.original: Correct answer! Yay!
subtitles.english: Correct answer! Yay!

subtitles.original: Go Gura! That was close!
subtitles.english: Go Gura! That was close!

subtitles.original: Okay, okay, okay, well...
subtitles.english: Okay, okay, okay, well...

subtitles.original: ...I still have one more question though.
subtitles.english: ...I still have one more question though.

subtitles.original: You're a winner, chicken dinner from the chicken, let's go!
subtitles.english: You're a winner, chicken dinner from the chicken, let's go!

subtitles.original: I think we're four for four so far.
subtitles.english: I think we're four for four so far.

subtitles.original: Yeah we are, but I guess my questions were a little bit too easy.
subtitles.english: Yeah we are, but I guess my questions were a little bit too easy.

subtitles.original: So for the next question, you will have to answer correctly otherwise...
subtitles.english: So for the next question, you will have to answer correctly otherwise...

subtitles.original: Otherwise? Oh damn it.
subtitles.english: Otherwise? Oh damn it.

subtitles.original: Otherwise there will be... yeah, it will be all or nothing.
subtitles.english: Otherwise there will be... yeah, it will be all or nothing.

subtitles.original: Is it all or nothing? Changing the rules on us.
subtitles.english: Is it all or nothing? Changing the rules on us.

subtitles.original: Can we double down? Do we get dessert too?
subtitles.english: Can we double down? Do we get dessert too?

subtitles.original: Of course, of course! All right, let's do it.
subtitles.english: Of course, of course! All right, let's do it.

subtitles.original: Excellent, excellent, last question!
subtitles.english: Excellent, excellent, last question!

subtitles.original: And how should we do this? Hmm...
subtitles.english: And how should we do this? Hmm...

subtitles.original: I want your separate answers.
subtitles.english: I want your separate answers.

subtitles.original: Huh? What happened? Wait, was changing the rules...
subtitles.english: Huh? What happened? Wait, was changing the rules...

subtitles.original: I want... no, I just want to see if you both get it right without hearing the other's answer first.
subtitles.english: I want... no, I just want to see if you both get it right without hearing the other's answer first.

subtitles.original: Okay, I'll take off my headphones. I'm out.
subtitles.english: Okay, I'll take off my headphones. I'm out.

subtitles.original: Okay, okay, okay, ma'am.
subtitles.english: Okay, okay, okay, ma'am.

subtitles.original: But wait, no, how do I give you a sign that you should come back?
subtitles.english: But wait, no, how do I give you a sign that you should come back?

subtitles.original: Whatever, just bring it back in in 30 seconds, okay?
subtitles.english: Whatever, just bring it back in in 30 seconds, okay?

subtitles.original: Okay, do like... throw up some kind of weird hand symbol.
subtitles.english: Okay, do like... throw up some kind of weird hand symbol.

subtitles.original: Ah okay, I'll do this. Do a little heart, yeah.
subtitles.english: Ah okay, I'll do this. Do a little heart, yeah.

subtitles.original: And then I'll come back. All right, bye. I'm taking off my headphones.
subtitles.english: And then I'll come back. All right, bye. I'm taking off my headphones.

subtitles.original: Bye! Gawr Gura!
subtitles.english: Bye! Gawr Gura!

subtitles.original: I actually have a feeling you'll get this one right.
subtitles.english: I actually have a feeling you'll get this one right.

subtitles.original: Really? Okay.
subtitles.english: Really? Okay.

subtitles.original: Spell out for me without thinking too much. You have to say it quickly.
subtitles.english: Spell out for me without thinking too much. You have to say it quickly.

subtitles.original: Auf wiedersehen.
subtitles.english: Auf wiedersehen.

subtitles.original: Spell auf wiedersehen
subtitles.english: Spell auf wiedersehen

subtitles.original: Go! Auf... A-U-F. Auf...
subtitles.english: Go! Auf... A-U-F. Auf...

subtitles.original: A-U-F, wiedersehen. V-I-E-D-E-R...
subtitles.english: A-U-F, wiedersehen. V-I-E-D-E-R...

subtitles.original: ...wiedersehen, S-E-N, S-E-U-N, S-E-N, auf...
subtitles.english: ...wiedersehen, S-E-N, S-E-U-N, S-E-N, auf...

subtitles.original: ...da... A-U-F. Auf is the first part.
subtitles.english: ...da... A-U-F. Auf is the first part.

subtitles.original: Wiedersehen. V-I-E-D-E-R...
subtitles.english: Wiedersehen. V-I-E-D-E-R...

subtitles.original: ...S-E-N, S-E-Y. Ah! It's hard to follow!
subtitles.english: ...S-E-N, S-E-Y. Ah! It's hard to follow!

subtitles.original: It's hard to follow! Final answer, go!
subtitles.english: It's hard to follow! Final answer, go!

subtitles.original: A-U-F.
subtitles.english: A-U-F.

subtitles.original: V.
subtitles.english: V.

subtitles.original: I-E-D-E-R S-E-E-N.
subtitles.english: I-E-D-E-R S-E-E-N.

subtitles.original: Wrong! Boo-boom!
subtitles.english: Wrong! Boo-boom!

subtitles.original: No! Okay Calli come back, Calli come back.
subtitles.english: No! Okay Calli come back, Calli come back.

subtitles.original: All I heard was wrong. Is it that hard of a question? Throw it at me, Kiara.
subtitles.english: All I heard was wrong. Is it that hard of a question? Throw it at me, Kiara.

subtitles.original: Now Calli recently had a lot of fun learning German with me, so you might...
subtitles.english: Now Calli recently had a lot of fun learning German with me, so you might...

subtitles.original: ...you might get this too.
subtitles.english: ...you might get this too.

subtitles.original: Fuck! The German question.
subtitles.english: Fuck! The German question.

subtitles.original: Yes! All right, good luck buddy.
subtitles.english: Yes! All right, good luck buddy.

subtitles.original: Spell, and you have to do it quickly, okay? No thinking.
subtitles.english: Spell, and you have to do it quickly, okay? No thinking.

subtitles.original: Spell my end greeting, auf wiedersehen.
subtitles.english: Spell my end greeting, auf wiedersehen.

subtitles.original: No! Stop! Don't! A-V...
subtitles.english: No! Stop! Don't! A-V...

subtitles.original: ...I-V... wait no! No! Shit! Damn it girl, come on!
subtitles.english: ...I-V... wait no! No! Shit! Damn it girl, come on!

subtitles.original: Auf wiedersehen... uh, fuck! That's too hard of a question!
subtitles.english: Auf wiedersehen... uh, fuck! That's too hard of a question!

subtitles.original: I thought this was a Kiara quiz, not a spelling bee!
subtitles.english: I thought this was a Kiara quiz, not a spelling bee!

subtitles.original: Chicken! A-V, arrivederci, arrivederci, grazie!
subtitles.english: Chicken! A-V, arrivederci, arrivederci, grazie!

subtitles.original: Mama mia! Final answer! V... no! Um...
subtitles.english: Mama mia! Final answer! V... no! Um...

subtitles.original: R... no wait, it's not arrivederci, it's auf wiedersehen.
subtitles.english: R... no wait, it's not arrivederci, it's auf wiedersehen.

subtitles.original: A-V... I'll give you ten more seconds!
subtitles.english: A-V... I'll give you ten more seconds!

subtitles.original: Come on, bonehead! A-V...
subtitles.english: Come on, bonehead! A-V...

subtitles.original: ...R-E-R... wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!
subtitles.english: ...R-E-R... wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!

subtitles.original: No!
subtitles.english: No!

subtitles.original: Wrong! What the fuck!
subtitles.english: Wrong! What the fuck!
